viewData.name: PhiLashes Isolation Tweezers
viewData.short_description: Perfect for isolating the eyelashes in the inner and outer corners of the eye, with ultimate precision. Gives you the power to separate the eyelashes individually and isolate them. Simple posture, positioning and adjustment for the smallest area
viewData.long_description: Perfect for isolating the eyelashes in the inner and outer corners of the eye, with ultimate precision. Gives you the power to separate the eyelashes individually and isolate them. Simple posture, positioning and adjustment for the smallest area. Made of high quality stainless steel.
